data.description: Enter the 4 bedroom, 1 1/2 bath home in awe from the natural lite of the enclosed 4 season porch. The breakfast peninsula divides but lends a glimpse into the beautifully updated kitchen with newer appliances. The hardwood floors are fitting & have been refinished to shine throughout. The sliding glass door will lead you into the privacy enclosed backyard oasis. The attached double insulated and heated garage to keep the chill out during out long winter months. The hot & cold spickets is convenient for detailing your vehicle or all those 'at home' projects. Roof was replaced in August 2023!
